text: Jung Eun-woo (born Jung Dong-jin on April 10, 1986) is a South Korean actor. He has starred in television dramas such as One Well-Raised Daughter (2013-2014) and The Return of Hwang Geum-bok (2015). ==Personal life== Jang dated actress Park Han-byul. == Filmography == === Television series === {| class="wikitable" style="width:600px" |- ! width=10|Year !
